snippet.title: THE MAGIC CIRCLE - LAUNCH TRAILER
snippet.description:
IT'S TIME, BOSS. HELP ME ESCAPE FROM DEVELOPMENT HELL. 

Available now on Steam (try the free demo!): http://store.steampowered.com/app/323380/ 

A dark comedy about the creators of unfinished games, starring James Urbaniak (Venture Bros, American Splendor), Stephen Russell (Thief Series, Skyrim), Ashly Burch (Borderlands 2, HAWP),  Karen Dyer (Resident Evil 5) ... and YOU. Can you out-think the game gods? Can you ship a game from the inside?

The Magic Circle was released July 9th, 2015 - but only you can say "When It's Done."
